snippet.title: Optmemus
snippet.description:
Hi, i'm Optmemus, I started this channel to make random memes, but now, I don't really know what I'm doing.

I like to hop on trends, anything that can get me clicks, I WILL POST ABOUT it ! 
Oh marvel released a new serie ? Cast a new actor ?  i'll give my opinion! 
A video game that I play released something new ? I might talk about it !!
Some beauty guru screwed up ? i'll definitely sh*t on them here !
Some celebrity is on the news ? hmm...lemme get their community to click on my vids !
Wait..is that...is that a viral meme ? I.WILL.MILK.THAT.COW.UNTIL.IT'S.DRY.

Im also here for a good time, not a long time, but i'll try to stick around to post here and then !

But most importantly, don't take anything I post seriously, this is just harmess banter !
This channel is for entertainment purposes only.
PLEASE DO NOT SEND HATE TO ANYONE MENTIONED IN MY VIDEOS.
